This is one of two keys required
to launch the Eclipse Cannon.

00:44:09.211 --> 00:44:11.518
The other is locked
inside GUN headquarters.

00:44:11.692 --> 00:44:13.563
Once we have both.

00:44:13.738 --> 00:44:16.566
