<i>To prevent the vault from ever
being accessed by a ring.</i>

00:50:55.878 --> 00:50:58.838
<i>all images and schematics have
been wiped from GUN's database.</i>

00:50:59.012 --> 00:51:01.058
So for the last leg
of this heist...

00:51:02.320 --> 00:51:04.278
we're going in blind.

00:51:08.978 --> 00:51:10.197
Sorry.

00:51:10.371 --> 00:51:11.894
Okay. I'm just gonna say it.

