Guys. are you ready for me yet?
I've been waiting here all day.

00:53:16.584 --> 00:53:19.413
Sonic.
we literally just started.

00:53:19.587 --> 00:53:21.807
Tom. Maddie.
are you in position and ready?

00:53:21.981 --> 00:53:24.113
- We were born ready.
